### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Leaderboard with custom count
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard?count=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Add Score
POST {{baseUrl}}/score
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "player": "Grace",
    "score": 3300
}

### WebSocket Connection
# To connect via WebSocket, use the following URL in your WebSocket client:
# ws://localhost:3000
#
# The server will send messages in the following format:
# {
#   "type": "leaderboard_update",
#   "leaderboard": [
#     { "player": "Alice", "score": 1000 },
#     { "player": "Bob", "score": 900 },
#     ...
#   ]
# }
